@startuml
title BEACON - System Context (C1)

!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Context.puml

Person(admin, "Admin")
System(beacon, "BEACON", "IoT Wi-Fi analytics cluster")

System_Ext(wifi, "Building Wi-Fi Infrastructure", "Wi-Fi environment that probes measure")
System_Ext(iperf, "iPerf Server", "Throughput and latency test endpoint")
System_Ext(ntp, "NTP / DNS", "Time sync and name resolution services")

Rel(admin, beacon, "Configure probes and view dashboards", "GraphQL + Grafana")
Rel(beacon, wifi, "Collect Wi-Fi metrics")
Rel(beacon, iperf, "Run active throughput and latency tests")
Rel(beacon, ntp, "Time sync and name resolution")

note right of beacon
  Deployables inside BEACON:
  • Raspberry Pi probe agents
  • GraphQL API + config store
  • Prometheus + Grafana stack
end note

note right of iperf
  Optional component for active testing.
  Only needed if you want to run
  throughput or latency tests.
end note

@enduml